Discover a function that takes an array of numbers as input and returns the sum of all the even numbers in
the array.

CODE:
<?php
function sumEvenNumbers($arr) {
    $sum = 0;
    foreach ($arr as $num) {
        if ($num % 2 == 0) {   // Check if number is even
            $sum += $num;
        }
    }
    return $sum;
}

// Example usage
$numbers = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8];
echo "Sum of even numbers: " . sumEvenNumbers($numbers);
?>

OUTPUT:
Sum of even numbers: 20
